<collectingRegion box="[736,828,439,466]" country="China" name="Qinghai" pageId="18" pageNumber="119">Qinghai</collectingRegion>
) (
<figureCitation box="[851,935,439,465]" captionStart="FIGURES 25–28" captionStartId="8.[151,264,1905,1929]" captionTargetBox="[189,1398,181,1880]" captionTargetId="figure-20@8.[189,1398,181,1881]" captionTargetPageId="8" captionText="FIGURES 25–28. Distribution of Pseudepipona spp. 25, P. aldrichi (Fox, 1892); 26, P. herrichii (de Saussure, 1856); 27, P. kozhevnikovi (Kostylev, 1927); 28, P. tingjingliae Fateryga, sp. nov. (black dots), P. tricarinata (Kokujev, 1913) (white dots), and P. valentinae Fateryga, sp. nov. (grey dots)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6641253" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6641253/files/figure.png" pageId="18" pageNumber="119">Fig. 28</figureCitation>
